metadata.name: Elron Electronic Industries Ltd
metadata.description: Elron Ventures Ltd, a venture capital company, invest in early-stage ventures in cybersecurity, enterprise software, medical tech, and other sectors in Israel. It provides a range of operational and management support services. The company was formerly known as Elron Electronic Industries Ltd. and changed its name to Elron Ventures Ltd in January 2022. Elron Ventures Ltd was incorporated in 1961 and is based in Tel Aviv, Israel
